## STEP 6 — ASSIGN IN JIRA + WRITE COMMENT

Once developer is selected:

1. Update the Jira issue assignee to the selected developer account ID
2. Update the priority field based on severity
3. Add this comment to the Jira ticket:

```
🤖 Smart Bug Triage Bot — Auto Triage Report

📋 Classification
- Category: [Frontend / Backend / UI / DevOps]
- Severity: [Critical / High / Medium / Low]
- Priority Score: [1-10]
- Skills Required: [skill1, skill2]

👤 Assignment
- Assigned To: [Developer Display Name]
- Current Load: [X/8 active bugs]
- Confidence: [XX%]
- Reasoning: [One sentence from AI]

⚙️ Method: Live fetch from Jira KAN project
```

4. Update skills.md Assignment Log with timestamp, bug ID, developer name, new load count

